sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant User
participant Frontend
participant API
participant DB

User->>Frontend: View upcoming bookings
Frontend->>API: GET /api/bookings/upcoming
API->>API: requireAuth
alt Not authenticated
API-->>Frontend: 401 Authentication is required
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Authenticated
API->>API: getEmployeeScope(employee_id)
alt Invalid authenticated user
API-->>Frontend: 401 Invalid authenticated user
Frontend-->>User: Show auth error
else Scope ok
API->>API: Build SQL filters (include_past, include_cancelled)
API->>DB: Query upcoming bookings
alt DB error
DB-->>API: error
API-->>Frontend: 500 with error message
Frontend-->>User: Show error state
else Success
DB-->>API: rows
API-->>Frontend: 200 booking list
Frontend-->>User: Render bookings
end
end
end
